{"tid":1247932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民意戰開始了，諗清楚你地係咪仲要周街衝衝衝","createTime":"2019-06-21T09:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T09:48:25.000Z","uid":55851,"like":9,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7205d25a421430e259a4208ac4a81df1308a66e4","tid":1247932,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7aUeHiK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7aUeHiK.png&h=b95ce81f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雨革嘅教訓：<br />\n第一次衝➡️武力嘗試清場➡️民意支持示威者➡️未達成100%訴求➡️繼續佔/衝➡️政府放手比你佔飽佢➡️日日公佈數據話你阻交通/緊急服務➡️民意開始反彈➡️清場➡️收皮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好話咩各有各做，你而家毫無目的咁衝/佔，係消耗民意，係反效果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家要做嘅，係真正深耕細作，浸入地區組織，做文宣，統一戰線。出街周圍衝，不如組織攞返功能組別議席返嚟好過啦。"},{"pid":"2c92bcc893e1af67de46d54af2df9a654c9e205f","tid":1247932,"uid":264245,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:40:59.000Z","msg":"呢個講法唔岩，呢個case係警察有得開工又唔做野，射個波比示範者wo"},{"pid":"219ec3f1f093c4398149d36284fc72e0b69d0418","tid":1247932,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2c92bcc893e1af67de46d54af2df9a654c9e205f","tid":1247932,"uid":264245,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:40:59.000Z","msg":"呢個講法唔岩，呢個case係警察有得開工又唔做野，射個波比示範者wo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:41:47.000Z","msg":"而家咪唔做野比你地周圍佔囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10f99a1c9235faf5e88aeeba6d2ca5af0deb1a2","tid":1247932,"uid":20696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:41:49.000Z","msg":"咁你就「有意義有目的地衝而係唔會令香港人反感」有咩意見？"},{"pid":"3d947b19f69ca9a968f9468d6ed96281b09c0906","tid":1247932,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c92bcc893e1af67de46d54af2df9a654c9e205f","tid":1247932,"uid":264245,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:40:59.000Z","msg":"呢個講法唔岩，呢個case係警察有得開工又唔做野，射個波比示範者wo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:41: